grow a thicker neocortex.

00:54:40.590 --> 00:54:43.100 align:middle line:84%
And the cool thing
about these meditations,

00:54:43.100 --> 00:54:44.740 align:middle line:84%
it actually shrinks
the amygdala,

00:54:44.740 --> 00:54:47.030 align:middle line:84%
that fear processing
part of your brain.

00:54:47.030 --> 00:54:47.530 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Hm.

00:54:47.530 --> 00:54:48.200 align:middle line:90%
Interesting.

00:54:48.200 --> 00:54:50.150 align:middle line:84%
And I'm sure
electromagnetically,

00:54:50.150 --> 00:54:53.332 align:middle line:84%
