00:55:11.300 --> 00:55:12.010 align:middle line:90%
>>WALDMAN: Can do, yes.

00:55:12.010 --> 00:55:12.870 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Can do.

00:55:12.870 --> 00:55:15.182 align:middle line:84%
It is how negative thoughts
can damage the brain.

00:55:15.182 --> 00:55:15.890 align:middle line:90%
>>WALDMAN: Right.

00:55:15.890 --> 00:55:18.410 align:middle line:84%
