they are doing hurts other

00:55:56.220 --> 00:55:57.110 align:middle line:90%
individuals.

00:55:57.110 --> 00:55:57.900 align:middle line:90%
They don't get it.

00:55:57.900 --> 00:55:58.400 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Hm.

00:55:58.400 --> 00:56:00.954 align:middle line:84%
