parts of the brain.

00:56:06.340 --> 00:56:07.830 align:middle line:84%
And they're repairing
their brain.

00:56:07.830 --> 00:56:08.910 align:middle line:84%
>>WALDMAN: And
there's a problem too

00:56:08.910 --> 00:56:11.210 align:middle line:84%
